{
  "info": {
    "name": "COACOM SRL - API",
    "description": "Colección completa de endpoints del sistema COACOM SRL.\n\n**Flujo de uso:**\n1. Ejecuta `Login` para obtener el token\n2. El token se guarda automáticamente en la variable `{{token}}`\n3. Los demás endpoints usan el token automáticamente",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000/api"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Módulo de autenticación",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.accessToken);",
                  "    console.log('Token guardado exitosamente');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@coacom.bo\",\n  \"password\": \"tu-password-aqui\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Inicia sesión con email y contraseña.\n\n**Respuesta:** JWT token + datos del usuario.\n\nEl token se guarda automáticamente en la variable `{{token}}` para usarlo en los demás endpoints."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/profile",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "profile"]
            },
            "description": "Obtiene el perfil del usuario autenticado.\n\n**Requiere:** Token JWT (se envía automáticamente)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Change Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"currentPassword\": \"password-actual\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"nuevo-password-seguro\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/change-password",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "change-password"]
            },
            "description": "Cambia la contraseña del usuario autenticado.\n\n**Requiere:** Token JWT\n\n**Nota:** Después de cambiar la contraseña, el flag `mustChangePassword` se pone en `false`."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Users",
      "description": "Módulo de gestión de usuarios (solo Admin)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Users",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&limit=10",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1",
                  "description": "Página (default: 1)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "10",
                  "description": "Registros por página (default: 10, max: 100)"
                },
                {
                  "key": "search",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Buscar por nombre (firstName/lastName) o email",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "role",
                  "value": "technician",
                  "description": "Filtrar por rol: admin | general_manager | branch_manager | technician | client",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "branchId",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Filtrar por UUID de sucursal (branch)",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "isActive",
                  "value": "true",
                  "description": "Filtrar por estado: true | false",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Lista usuarios con paginación y filtros.\n\n**Roles permitidos:** Admin\n\n**Filtros opcionales:**\n- `search` — busca en firstName, lastName y email\n- `role` — filtra por rol (admin, general_manager, branch_manager, technician, client)\n- `branchId` — filtra por sucursal (branch)\n- `isActive` — filtra por estado (true/false)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Users - Search",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users?search=carlos&page=1&limit=10",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "search",
                  "value": "carlos"
                },
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "10"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Ejemplo: buscar usuarios por nombre 'carlos'."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Users - By Role",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users?role=technician&page=1&limit=10",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "role",
                  "value": "technician"
                },
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "10"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Ejemplo: listar solo técnicos (technician)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Users - Inactive",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users?isActive=false&page=1&limit=10",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "isActive",
                  "value": "false"
                },
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "10"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Ejemplo: listar solo usuarios inactivos."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User by ID",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "// Asegúrate de tener un userId válido en las variables"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "{{userId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Obtiene un usuario por su UUID.\n\n**Requiere:** `userId` en las variables de la colección."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create User",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', res.id);",
                  "    console.log('userId guardado:', res.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"firstName\": \"Carlos\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Mendoza\",\n  \"email\": \"cmendoza@coacom.bo\",\n  \"password\": \"Temporal123\",\n  \"role\": \"technician\",\n  \"branchId\": \"uuid-de-sucursal-aqui\",\n  \"specialty\": \"Hardware\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users"]
            },
            "description": "Crea un nuevo usuario con contraseña temporal.\n\n**Roles permitidos:** Admin\n\n**Campos:**\n- `firstName` (nombre, requerido, max 100)\n- `lastName` (apellido, requerido, max 100)\n- `email` (requerido, formato email)\n- `password` (requerido, min 6, max 72)\n- `role` (rol, requerido): admin | general_manager | branch_manager | technician | client\n- `branchId` (sucursal, opcional, UUID): requerido para branch_manager y technician\n- `specialty` (especialidad, opcional, max 100): solo para technician\n\n**Nota:** El usuario se crea con `mustChangePassword: true`. En su primer login deberá cambiar la contraseña.\n\nEl `userId` se guarda automáticamente en las variables."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Admin",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', res.id);",
                  "    console.log('Admin userId guardado:', res.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"firstName\": \"Admin\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Principal\",\n  \"email\": \"admin@coacom.bo\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin2026!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/admin",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "admin"]
            },
            "description": "Crea un usuario administrador.\n\n**Roles permitidos:** Admin\n\n**Campos:** Solo firstName (nombre), lastName (apellido), email y password.\nNo requiere branchId (sucursal) ni specialty (especialidad).\n\nSe crea con `mustChangePassword: false` y `role: admin` automáticamente."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create User - Branch Manager",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"firstName\": \"Laura\",\n  \"lastName\": \"Pérez\",\n  \"email\": \"lperez@coacom.bo\",\n  \"password\": \"Temporal123\",\n  \"role\": \"branch_manager\",\n  \"branchId\": \"uuid-de-sucursal-aqui\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users"]
            },
            "description": "Ejemplo: crear un Gerente de Sucursal (branch_manager, requiere branchId)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update User",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"firstName\": \"Carlos Alberto\",\n  \"specialty\": \"Redes\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "{{userId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Actualiza parcialmente un usuario.\n\n**Roles permitidos:** Admin\n\nSolo enviar los campos que se quieren cambiar."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Deactivate User",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/deactivate",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "{{userId}}", "deactivate"]
            },
            "description": "Desactiva un usuario (soft delete).\n\n**Roles permitidos:** Admin\n\nNo elimina el registro, solo pone `isActive = false`."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Activate User",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}/activate",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["users", "{{userId}}", "activate"]
            },
            "description": "Reactiva un usuario desactivado.\n\n**Roles permitidos:** Admin"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Branches",
      "description": "Módulo de gestión de sucursales (branches)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Branches",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/branches",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["branches"]
            },
            "description": "Lista todas las sucursales (branches) activas.\n\n**Roles permitidos:** Admin, General Manager"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Branch by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/branches/:id",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["branches", ":id"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "uuid-de-sucursal-aqui",
                  "description": "UUID de la sucursal (branch)"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Obtiene una sucursal (branch) por su UUID."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Branch",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Nueva Sucursal\",\n  \"city\": \"Santa Cruz\",\n  \"address\": \"Av. Principal #123\",\n  \"phone\": \"33445566\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/branches",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["branches"]
            },
            "description": "Crea una nueva sucursal (branch).\n\n**Roles permitidos:** Admin\n\n**Campos:**\n- `name` (nombre, requerido)\n- `city` (ciudad, requerido)\n- `address` (dirección, requerido)\n- `phone` (teléfono, opcional)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Branch",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Sucursal Actualizada\",\n  \"phone\": \"77889900\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/branches/:id",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["branches", ":id"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "uuid-de-sucursal-aqui",
                  "description": "UUID de la sucursal (branch)"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Actualiza parcialmente una sucursal (branch).\n\n**Roles permitidos:** Admin\n\nSolo enviar los campos que se quieren cambiar."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Deactivate Branch",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/branches/:id/deactivate",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["branches", ":id", "deactivate"],
              "variable": [
                {
                  "key": "id",
                  "value": "uuid-de-sucursal-aqui",
                  "description": "UUID de la sucursal (branch)"
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Desactiva una sucursal (branch). Soft delete.\n\n**Roles permitidos:** Admin"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}